description: Big map jam pack with 22 levels ranging from small to large, with veteran and beginner designers. Maps were made in 2 1/2 weeks, with hot sunny theming encouraged but not required. Includes custom start map with built-in difficulty selection. Uses Copper v1.19 (already included) and co-op supported. QuakeC source is also included, as well as some MAP source.
notes: UPDATE, 11 August 2022: This version has major bugs. The authors strongly recommend playing the v1.2 patched version instead.
Requires a modern engine / source port with increased limits.
title: Coppertone Summer Jam 2 v1.0
